    "The single syndrome cycle is illustrated in Fig. 2.",
    "The entire syndrome measurement circuit was composed to simultaneously minimize the number of gates used, optimize depth (including parallelizing register measurement with state initialization and with gate application, whenever possible), limit the propagation of errors and comply with the qubit-to-qubit connectivity layout offered by the Tanner graph.",
